
8-bit instructions?

SLO 00 RR VVVV Set low bits of register R
SHI 01 RR VVVV Set high bits of register R
MOV 1000 DD RR Copy register R to D
ADD 1001 DD RR Add register R to D
OR  1010 DD RR Add register R to D
AND 1011 DD RR Add register R to D
NOT 1100 DD RR Add register R to D
XOR 1101 DD RR Add register R to D
PRT 1111 XX RR Print register R

NOP = MOV RR RR
